  <!--Overview-->
	<p id="A">Hate crimes against Asians have increased within the US since the start of the pandemic. Asian Americans have
		been the recipient of “othering,” ridicule, and cruelty. Many Asian Americans have begun speaking out on their experience
		and how this sudden spike of hate crime against Asians is impacting them and how they nagivate through the world.</p>
</body>

